{"title":"一瓣心花","authors":["苏艺林"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一瓣心花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽芜湖县  苏艺林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呐喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有一根普普通通的气管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在魑魅魍魉的眼里——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是贮藏利剑的刀鞘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是飞出子弹的枪管。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凶手举起了刀子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的声音又怎么能切断？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你凭借着祖国的江河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时刻刻为真理呼喊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"申请书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的申请书为什么这样动人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的纸上写满激情的诗文："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为实现共产主义远大理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不中途动摇，直到献出我的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是我们听惯了的大话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是投机商廉价的保证——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，用血与火写在大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个标点，都象是流血的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}